title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 7 2022
description:
Will Clay win the bet with Buck? Washington Post breaks story that Feds are weighing tax and gun charges against Hunter Biden. Buck says, "They may say to Biden, 'You know you're going to have to pardon your son, but you're no longer politically viable now.' That's the brass-knuckling that might get used." Clay's take, "I am always trying to read the tea leaves of who's leaking and why they're leaking." It's almost Christmas buying season. Blake Masters kicks Mark Kelly's ass in debate. Biden pardons thousands convicted of marijuana possession.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
